            "text": "DOC.title.macStatus=\"MAC Status\",PROMPT.status.noMacInDevice=\"The current device has not written MAC and may conflict with other devices.\",wlan5ghtml.helper.title7_1=\"The length of the security key should be between 8 and 63 characters. Spaces, double quotes, single quotes, '\\\\' and '/' cannot be entered.\",DOC.lbl.usbMode=\"Negotiation Mode\",DOC.lte.currentBand=\"Current frequency band\",DOC.lbl.adbCloseTips=\"The Modem log function has been turned on. Please turn off the Modem log function before turning off the ADB function.\",DOC.lbl.battery_charging_timeout=\"The device charge timeouts, and the battery will be suspended for a period of time before continuing to charge.\",DOC.lbl.is_battery_temperature_abnormal=\"The device is in a high/low temperature environment, and temporarily stops charging to protect the battery safety\",DOC.lbl.meshSingleWifiDebug=\"Debug version can only connect to one wifi\",DOC.lbl.nervelightsOut=\"Never turn off the lights\",DOC.device.voipclient_version=\"VoIP Version\",TAB.voice.hotlineDialDelay=\"Hotline dialing delay\",DOC.lbl.ussi_tip=\"VoLTE is not registered, USSI is not allowed\",DOC.lbl.ussd_tip=\"VoLTE is not registered, USSD is not allowed\",DOC.lbl.wifiPower=\"Wi-Fi power\",DOC.lbl.performanceMode=\"Performance mode\",DOC.lbl.standardMode=\"Standard mode\",DOC.lbl.lowerMode=\"Energy-saving mode\",DOC.lbl.wifiAbnormality=\"Wi-Fi running status is abnormal\",CHECK.range.daylightSavingStartDate=\"Input range: 1~28\",CHECK.range.auto_off_time=\"Input range: 1~1440\",DOC.lbl.guest_wifi_auto_off_time=\"Automatic shutdown time\",DOC.lbl.guest_wifi_auto_off=\"The guest WIFI is automatically turned off\",DOC.lbl.FIRE_level=\"Firewall level configuration\",DOC.lbl.FIRE_level1=\"Low\",DOC.lbl.FIRE_level2=\"Medium\",DOC.lbl.FIRE_level3=\"High\",MENU.sys.wirelessInternetAuth=\"Wireless Internet Certification\",DOC.lbl.wirelessSwTipOpen=\"After the wireless Internet authentication is enabled, the terminal device needs to access the Internet through this product.\",DOC.lbl.wirelessSwTipClose=\"After the wireless Internet authentication is closed, there is no need to be certified when the terminal device is accessing the Internet through this product. Please operate according to the actual scenario requirements.\",PROMPT.tips.wirelessAlert=\"A single mobile phone number supports up to 5 certification text messages a day, and it is not certified within 30 days after successful certification.\",DOC.sys.autoMode=\"Auto mode\",DOC.lbl.wirelessAuthWifi=\"Wi-Fi wireless device Internet authentication\",DOC.lbl.wirelessAuthEth=\"ETH wired device Internet certification\",MENU.sys.wirelessAuth=\"Wireless authentication settings\",DOC.lbl.wirelessAuthSw=\"Wireless Internet authentication switch\",DOC.lbl.certifiedDevices=\"Certified equipment\",DOC.lbl.NoCertifiedDevices=\"Uncertified equipment\",DOC.lbl.clickOnAuthentication=\"Click to authenticate\",DOC.lbl.expirationDate=\"Expiration time\",TAB.advance.MascomePortal=\"Mascom ePortal\",TAB.sys.weakCellRsrpThreshold=\"RSRP threshold\",TAB.sys.weakCellLimit=\"Weak cell limit\",DOC.lbl.activeStatus=\"Activation status\",DOC.lbl.testCard=\"Test SIM\",DOC.lbl.seedCard=\"Seed SIM\",DOC.lbl.businessCard=\"Business SIM\",DOC.lbl.esimSwitch=\"eSIM Switch\",DOC.lbl.probeSetting=\"Industrial probe setup\",DOC.lbl.probeSettingSw=\"Industrial probe switch\",DOC.lbl.SN=\"SN\",DOC.lbl.wifiNumTip=\"Modifying the number of Wi-Fi connections in the device may cause the terminals that have Wi-Fi to be disconnected. If the terminal does not have automatic Wi-Fi connection, try to connect manually.\",DOC.vpn.greDefaultGW=\"Default Gateway Switch\",MENU.sys.autoTimeSet=\"Automatic lights-off time setting\",MENU.sys.autoTimeSetTip=\"After turning on, the lights will be turned off according to this scheduled time at any time period.\",MENU.sys.intelTimeSet=\"Intelligent lights-off time setting\",MENU.sys.intelTimeSetTip=\"Only during this period can th