s\",CHECK.tip.filterRlueEmpty=\"There are no rules in the list to clean up\",CHECK.tip.isDataNull=\"No data in the list\",CHECK.tip.filterRlueSame=\"The rule already exists in the list\",CHECK.tip.notSave=\"Tip: Rule(s) is not saved\",CHECK.tip.wifiSameOpen=\"Tip: 5 GHz preference is turned on, Wi-Fi parameters cannot be modified\",CHECK.tip.wifiClientOpen=\"Tip: The current Wi-Fi is in Client mode, and the Wi-Fi parameters in AP mode are invalid\",CHECK.tip.arpWarning=\"Important Hint\",CHECK.tip.arpWarningText=\"Non-professionals do not recommend using this function. If the device is abnormal after operation, you can press the factory reset button to restore.\",CHECK.tip.MTUWarningText=\"*Non-professionals do not recommend to modify the MTU value, which may cause Internet failure\",CHECK.tip.timeWaringText=\"If the time zone of your system is inconsistent with the current time zone, the setting may not take effect.\",CHECK.tip.loginTimeout=\"Login Timeout !\",CHECK.tip.portSetting=\"Set the port carefully. Do not use the port occupied by the system. The wrong setting can be restored by restoring the factory settings\",CHECK.tip.routerWarningText=\"*Non-professionals are not recommended to modify the bound network bridge, which may cause Internet access failure\",CHECK.tip.mixWanModeText=\"Hybrid mode requires link detection function to be turned on to use\",CHECK.tip.SMSOutBoxFull=\"*The inbox is full, please clear your inbox to prevent you from not being able to receive new text messages\",CHECK.tip.SMSInBoxFull=\"Outbox is full and new SMS cannot be sent\",CHECK.tip.SMSFlightMode=\"Airplane mode is turned on and new SMS cannot be sent\",DOC.antenna.auto=\"Auto\",DOC.apn.ipRangeLimit=\"The start IP cannot be greater than the end IP\",DOC.apn.IPPool=\"IP address pool format error\",DOC.apn.setting_apn=\"Main APN\",DOC.apn.settingMultiApn=\"Multiple APN Settings\",DOC.apn.emptyMultiApn=\"Does not support multiple APNs\",DOC.apn.apnList=\"APN List\",DOC.apn.addAPN=\