When selected, APN information will be obtained from the network side and activated\",DOC.at.helper=\"This page can test AT commands and get response. Before the test, you need to input the AT command, and then press the send button, please wait for a short period of time for the response(the cost time depends on the AT command).\",DOC.at.input=\"Input AT\",DOC.at.requiredAT=\"AT command can not be empty\",DOC.at.response=\"AT Response\",DOC.at.title=\"AT Command\",DOC.btn.addRule=\"Add Rule\",DOC.btn.apply=\"Apply\",DOC.btn.applyRules=\"Save And Apply Rules\",DOC.btn.applyRule=\"Apply Rule\",DOC.btn.browse=\"Browse...\",DOC.btn.clear=\"Clear\",DOC.btn.clearAll=\"Clear List\",DOC.btn.clearAllRules=\"Clear All Rules\",DOC.btn.close=\"Close\",DOC.btn.connect=\"Connect\",DOC.btn.deleteSelected=\"Delete Selected\",DOC.btn.disconnect=\"Disconnect\",DOC.btn.exportCfg=\"Export Configuration\",DOC.btn.getClientTime=\"Get Client Time\",DOC.btn.syncClientTime=\"Synchronize client time\",DOC.btn.saveTime=\"Save and update network time\",DOC.btn.loadCfg=\"Import Configuration\",DOC.btn.login=\"Login\",DOC.btn.loginAuto=\"Automatic updates to provide a better user experience\",DOC.btn.refresh=\"Refresh\",DOC.btn.restore=\"Restore\",DOC.btn.restoreFactory=\"Restore\",DOC.btn.save=\"Save\",DOC.btn.reset=\"Unregister\",DOC.btn.savePin=\"Save\",DOC.btn.savePinOk=\"OK\",DOC.btn.send=\"Send\",DOC.btn.set=\"Set\",DOC.btn.confirm=\"Confirm\",DOC.btn.start=\"Start\",DOC.btn.stop=\"Stop\",DOC.btn.update=\"Upgrade\",DOC.btn.update1=\"System Upgrade\",DOC.btn.update2=\"Configuration Upgrade\",DOC.btn.updatePinCancel=\"Cancel\",DOC.btn.updatePinOk=\"OK\",DOC.btn.upload=\"Upload\",DOC.btn.same5g=\"Sync 5 GHz\",DOC.btn.same24g=\"Sync 2.4 GHz\",DOC.btn.search=\"Search\",DOC.colon=\":\",DOC.comma=\",\",DOC.copyright=\"Copyright © {0} All Rights Reserved.\",DOC.ddl.signalLevelNone=\"No signal\",DOC.ddl.signalLevel0=\"Very Weak\",DOC.ddl.signalLevel1=\"Weak\",DOC.ddl.signalLevel2=\"Normal\",DOC.dd