sists of a maximum of 32 characters consisting of letters and numbers, case-sensitive.\",wlan5ghtml.helper.title4=\"Channel\",wlan5ghtml.helper.item4=\"Settings the channel used by the wireless router, the default is auto.\",wlan5ghtml.helper.title5=\" Wi-Fi Mode\",wlan5ghtml.helper.item5=\"Set the working mode used by wireless router\",wlan5ghtml.helper.item5_2=\"Set the working mode used by wireless router\",wlan5ghtml.helper.title6=\"Authentication Type\",wlan5ghtml.helper.item6=\"Wi-Fi connection selection of security forms\",wlan5ghtml.helper.title7=\"Security Key\",wlan5ghtml.helper.item7=\"Set a wireless network password.\",wlan5ghtml.helper.title8=\"TX Power\",wlan5ghtml.helper.item8=\"Professionals settings, users generally do not change.\",wlan5ghtml.helper.title8_2=\"Max Station\",wlan5ghtml.helper.item8_2=\"The maximum number of users connected to this device.\",wlan5ghtml.helper.title12=\"Bandwidth\",wlan5ghtml.helper.item12=\"Be able to select 20 MHz, 20/40 MHz or 40 MHz\",wlan5ghtml.helper.item12_2=\"Be able to select 20 MHz, 40 MHz or 80 MHz\",wlan5ghtml.helper.item13=\"2.4 GHz and 5 GHz signals are displayed together, and the faster 5 GHz is preferred under the same signal.Turn off this switch to set separately.\",wlan5ghtml.helper.item14=\"Press and hold the WPS key for 6 seconds on the device to start the 2.4 GHz WPS function. If there is no key, try to start the WPS function on the web page\",wlan5ghtml.helper.item15=\"Press and hold the WPS key on the device for 1-3 seconds to start the 5 GHz WPS function. If there is no key, please try to start the WPS function on the webpage\",wlan5ghtml.helper.item17=\"Dynamic frequency selection\",DOC.lbl.wpsopen4G=\"(Need to turn on 2.4 GHz Wi-Fi broadcast)\",DOC.lbl.wpsopen5G=\"(Need to turn on 5 GHz Wi-Fi broadcast)\",DOC.wiredSetting.wiredType=\"Connection Method:\",DOC.wiredSetting.ipType=\"IP Method\",DOC.wiredSetting.pppoeType=\"PPPoE Method\",DOC.wiredSetting.ipProtocolType=\"IP Protocol Version:\",D