and alternate DNS server, etc. The IP address must be entered in the correct format.\",DOC.wiredSetting.item5=\"The maximum transmission unit is used to inform the other party of the maximum size of the data service unit that can be accepted. Do not modify it unless necessary.\",network.helper.item1=\"Only supports LTE network\",network.helper.item2=\"Support SA, NSA, LTE network\",network.helper.item3=\"Support NSA, LTE network\",network.helper.item4=\"Only supports SA network\",network.helper.item5=\"Please enter the MAC address to be cloned. If the parameter is empty, it means that the MAC address cloning function is not enabled\",network.helper.item6=\"Supports 4G and 5G networks\",DOC.lbl.trafficSetting=\"Traffic Setting\",DOC.lbl.trafficLimit=\"Set Traffic Limit\",DOC.lbl.trafficRestriction=\"Traffic Restrictions\",DOC.lbl.trafficStastDay=\"Start Date Of Billing Cycle\",DOC.lbl.trafficRemaining=\"Remaining\",DOC.lbl.trafficLimitSwitch=\"Limit Switch\",DOC.lbl.trafficMounthUsed=\"Used This Month:\",DOC.lbl.trafficMounthRemaining=\"Remaining Traffic This Month:\",DOC.lbl.trafficSureClear=\"Are you sure you want to clear the statistical traffic?\",DOC.lbl.trafficTips=\"Note: After the traffic limit function is enabled, when the traffic usage exceeds the set threshold this month, the 5G network communication will be automatically closed and switched to the wired network\",DOC.lbl.communicationPolicySetting=\"Communication Policy Settings\",DOC.lbl.routerBinding=\"Route Binding Settings\",DOC.lbl.batchAdd=\"Batch Add\",DOC.lbl.batchAddTips=\"Separate each mac with comma\",DOC.lbl.addMacFail=\"The above mac was not successfully added\",DOC.lbl.routerBinding1=\"Bridge Binding Primary APN\",DOC.lbl.routerBinding2=\"Wired WAN Binding Bridge\",DOC.lbl.routerBinding3=\"2.4 GHz Wi-Fi Bridge Binding\",DOC.lbl.routerBinding4=\"5 GHz Wi-Fi Bridge Binding\",DOC.lbl.routerBinding5=\"APN/WAN Primary Binding Bridge\",DOC.lbl.routerBinding7=\"APN/WAN Primary Binding Bridge\",DOC.