",DOC.lbl.uisSwtich=\"UIS switch\",DOC.lbl.bssAddress=\"BSS address\",DOC.lbl.bssPort=\"BSS port\",DOC.lbl.abiAddress=\"ABI capability platform address\",DOC.lbl.abiPort=\"ABI Capability Platform Port\",DOC.lbl.abiBackAdd=\"Alternate Capability Platform Address\",DOC.lbl.abiBackPort=\"Alternate Capability Platform Port\",DOC.lbl.scg=\"SCG Limit\",DOC.lbl.scgstr=\"AT parameters\",DOC.lbl.scgstrExplain=\"<li> Please enter four digits separated by commas, such as '1,2,2,2' </li> <li>The first digit: the unit is minutes, the duration of monitoring SCG failure </li> <li> The second digit: the maximum number of SCG failures within the monitoring period, such as 2 times. </li> <li> The third digit: the unit is minutes, and the recorded occurrences will not be reported within the penalty time The B1/B2 measurement report of the NR cell where the SCG fails.</li> <li>The fourth digit: the unit is minutes, the time to judge whether to release the penalty of the NR cell after the penalty period. For example, 1 minute, there is no 1 minute after the establishment of the ENDC If SCG fails, the NR cell is considered to be back to normal</li>\",DOC.lbl.batteryPower=\"Battery Remaining:\",DOC.lbl.batteryCharge=\"Charging:\",DOC.lbl.batteryChargeQuickly=\"Quick charge\",PROMPT.status.apnStatus=\"Cannot open multiple VPNs at the same time, there will be conflicts between functions\",PROMPT.tips.simError=\"Please use the correct operator's SIM\",MENU.settingWifi.headOD=\"OD Wi-Fi Settings\",MENU.settingWifi.wifiOD=\"OD 2.4 GHz Wi-Fi Settings\",MENU.settingWifi.wifiAdvanceOD=\"OD 2.4 GHz Wi-Fi Advanced Settings\",DOC.networkModeHelper.arp_item1=\"Turning on this function mainly realizes that IP can only correspond to one MAC, but one MAC can correspond to multiple IPs\",DOC.networkModeHelper.arp_item2=\"1. The IP+MAC of the connected device is the same as that configured in the device to be tested, and the gateway can be accessed normally; (PASS)\",DOC.networkModeHelper.arp_item3=\"2. The IP+MAC of the connected device is inconsistent with the IP configured in the device to be tested, but the MAC is the same, and the gateway can be accessed; (PASS)\",DOC.networkModeHelper.arp_item4=\"3. If the IP+MAC of the connected device is the same as the IP configured in the device to be tested, but the MAC is inconsistent, the gateway cannot be accessed; (FAIL)\",DOC.networkModeHelper.arp_item5=\"This function needs to be actively bound with the DHCP function. When dynamically assigning IP, the MAC address bound to the static IP is set, and only the corresponding IP can be assigned to the connected PC device.\",DOC.lbl.tr069ConnetStatus116=\"Data sending failed\",DOC.lbl.tr069ConnetStatus117=\"Receive packets\",DOC.lbl.tr069ConnetStatus118=\"The packet header data parsing is abnormal, and the complete data packet may not be received\",DOC.lbl.tr069ConnetStatus119=\"Unknown error status packet\",DOC.lbl.tr069ConnetStatus120=\"No header data can be collected\",DOC.lbl.tr069ConnetStatus121=\"No packet data can be collected\",DOC.lbl.tr069ConnetStatus122=\"Data parsing, failed to apply for space\",DOC.lbl.tr069ConnetStatus123=\"Data parsing, unsupported rpc\",DOC.lbl.tr069ConnetStatus124=\"Session could not be established (ACS URL is malformed)\",DOC.lbl.tr069ConnetStatus125=\"400 Invalid request\",DOC.lbl.tr069ConnetStatus126=\"403 Forbidden\",DOC.lbl.tr069ConnetStatus127=\"404 The requested resource does not exist\",DOC.lbl.tr069ConnetStatus128=\"405 Resource forbidden\",DOC.lbl.tr069ConnetStatus129=\"406 Unacceptable\",DOC.lbl.tr069ConnetStatus130=\"410 never available\",DOC.lbl.tr069ConnetStatus131=\"412 Prerequisite failed\",DOC.lbl.tr069ConnetStatus132=\"414 Request URI too long\",DOC.lbl.tr069ConnetStatus133=\"500 An unexpected error occurred on the server\",PROMPT.status.error502PLNM=\"Please confirm whether the selected PLMN is allowed to stay on the network\",DOC.net.coneNatSettings=\"NAT Settings\",DOC.net.coneNatType=\"NAT type\",DOC.net.coneNatSport